#: ../../ecommerce/shopper_experience/paypal.rst:22
msgid "Now enter the menu **My selling tools**."
msgstr "Ora inserire il menu **i Miei strumenti di vendita**."

#: ../../ecommerce/shopper_experience/paypal.rst:27
